            <title>
                <![CDATA[ AI+IoT+数字孪生！大吨位智能定位牵引装备制造取得新突破 ]]>
            </title>
            <link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTk4NDQxMg==&mid=2649427284&idx=2&sn=d34361fe6ba9e928980b8d852027efb5&chksm=bf2c8127885b08313f830c69f78e3c9481da7f3cefd54edb71dc989ee46ad7b0171bd380436b#rd</link>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[ 3月27日由中国海油牵头研发的1500kN（千牛）智能定位绞车系统在天津集成完工并进入调试阶段标志着我国大吨位智能定位牵引装备制造取得新突破绞车系统是海洋工程作业的关键装备，主要用于系泊固定、拖曳牵引、打捞救援‌等任务，是海洋科考调查、海洋资源开发、海洋工程作业等领域不可或缺的重要装备，被业内誉为船... ]]>
            </description>
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[ <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.20055710306406685" data-s="300,640" data-w="1077" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wpgKmKoa7iad6zIjPU1FAZZnibrAWyJGsItBdQwkWdRFqCVIvt5Mv4O7L50lC5d4rpmxkgib66AqP3lf445iatG5eyPlPxIZl3cQGlRoKWIk5Jg/640?wx_fmt=gif"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">3月27日</span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">由中国海油牵头研发的</span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">1500kN（千牛）智能定位绞车系统</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">在天津集成完工并进入调试阶段</span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">标志着我国大吨位</span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">智能定位牵引装备制造</span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">取得新突破</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-ratio="0.667032967032967" data-s="300,640" data-w="910" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iadsyZLhT6yWmzWPABkcUsMM178RibHicVuIDJqHR4bGBTrPO9WDKTullz3UVyfJDFmrtEgt2LXZ1xLP0qZelq4NIpWPZvlYUmdWM/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">绞车系统是海洋工程作业的关键装备，主要用于系泊固定、拖曳牵引、打捞救援‌等任务，是海洋科考调查、海洋资源开发、海洋工程作业等领域不可或缺的重要装备，被业内誉为船舶的“力量枢纽”。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.6663007683863886" data-s="300,640" data-w="911" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iacJicEvzHAaBy0S7cs4Q2eBaZDJ8ybeu5KibycvPWhnEPfSrm2k3rNx9pia4bhuoibhkESBxbt2q6icMAY06bXE01H8Y2vz4xJjLVOI/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">传统绞车系统在作业过程中高度依赖人工操作，通常需要多名操作人员协同配合完成启停、调速、对位、监护等工序，可能因响应滞后、工况适应性弱、监测能力不足带来作业风险。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.7512376237623762" data-s="300,640" data-w="808" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iacDULw7OIcSx6RS7KEbANGdH5J48TkE4HoGmDBKA24KVKUVI3DtjcscZ2KKqia2oXUwzvSHCaet4Qj6NefnkYo13PPPql9DNRjU/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">本次集成完工的智能定位绞车系统</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">由智能控制中心、绞车主机、动力站等部分构成</span></span></strong><span leaf="">，集成姿态传感、动态预警、离线自治等辅助模块，并引入物联网（IoT）智能控制、AI视觉识别、数字孪生仿真和高精度伺服控制技术，</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">可实现作业过程精准定位、智能调控与动态监测</span></span></strong><span leaf="">，有效提升复杂工况下作业安全和效率。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.667032967032967" data-s="300,640" data-w="910" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iac9F7VlHzaUUJ2nHiaur2JorFNownFtQzWcpjX4NIMImugZo9QK8qasywhrictrPecr8l8k17f5ytKbAawmctpjVtT49yehQHArI/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">该系统单机额定拉力达1500kN，设计寿命30年，核心软件与硬件基本实现自主研发。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">面对大吨位绞车系统在海洋极端工况下控制难度大、重载冲击大、盐雾腐蚀强等挑战，项目团队攻克多设备协同、远程通信、深水传感及自适应调节等多项行业技术难题，关键部件采用高强度、高韧性特种合金钢，可有效满足极端环境下高强度、高负重作业需求，大幅提升装备稳定性。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(126, 122, 1