            <description>
                <![CDATA[ “朱贺，总分第一！”2025年9月捷报从中山传来在中国海油第十三届职业技能竞赛燃气轮机运行值班员竞赛中气电集团珠海电厂运行部值长朱贺获得总分第一金牌的背后是他十余年扎根一线精益求精的漫长跋涉那些黑暗中的孤勇微光中的洞察都化为他成长道路上的坐标熠熠闪耀从检修到运行的转身2013年，还在实习期的朱贺从珠... ]]>
            </description>
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[ <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 2em;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.20055710306406685" data-s="300,640" data-w="1077" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wpgKmKoa7iad6zIjPU1FAZZnibrAWyJGsItBdQwkWdRFqCVIvt5Mv4O7L50lC5d4rpmxkgib66AqP3lf445iatG5eyPlPxIZl3cQGlRoKWIk5Jg/640?wx_fmt=gif"></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.206" data-s="300,640" data-w="1000" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iadPYl9nTSxousiafibg8ugWWWpKmNSS723U0Khn4xsa45A1uX7zYuRibFUgibK8XvoR7mFcGicg9l3KfAGiaQdiaJIxuvqwCO8tGC8I1w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;padding: 0px 7px;font-size: 18px;"><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“朱贺，总分第一！”</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">2025年9月</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">捷报从中山传来</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">在中国海油第十三届职业技能竞赛</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">燃气轮机运行值班员竞赛中</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">气电集团珠海电厂运行部值长朱贺</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">获得总分第一</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">金牌的背后</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">是他十余年扎根一线</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">精益求精的漫长跋涉</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">那些黑暗中的孤勇</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">微光中的洞察</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">都化为他成长道路上的坐标</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">熠熠闪耀</span></span></p></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);margin: -3px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="transform: rotateZ(315deg);-webkit-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-moz-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-o-transform: rotateZ(315deg);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 26px;height: 26px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 7px;border-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);background-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 3px inset;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 4px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(95, 156, 239);letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">从检修到运行的转身</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(178, 210, 240);height: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;padding: 0px 7px;font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">2013年，还在实习期的朱贺从珠海电厂设备检修岗调整至集控运行岗。彼时，珠海电厂正由建设期转向运营期，而运行岗位，就是驾驭这座电厂的中枢。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“工作岗位的调整对我来说，像是由‘修飞机’到‘开飞机’的转变，跨度很大。”</span></span></strong><span leaf="">初到运行岗位的朱贺，面对集控室内满屏的英文参数、错综复杂的系统图和实时跳动的曲线信号，压力陡增。几次阶段性考试，他的成绩都徘徊在及格线边缘，鲜红的分数像一根根尖刺，扎得他有些泄气。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iaevbSnD2ia5iaXkUibp5FsRJnMOs8cTHh7pPgumElKib349fLVncmAXuRD8icNcuqXicohJlDpicWryF9lf41iasIBgKTtyTVjxQ2KhdlI/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><section style="line-height: 2;padding: 0px 7px;font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他没有被挫折压垮，反而摸索出一套“笨办法”——白天，他寸步不离地跟着师傅巡检，将每一个操作细节、每一个异常参数工工整整地记在随身携带的笔记本上；夜里，别人休息时，他对照着厚厚的运行规程与盘根错节的系统图，把白天的疑问逐一复盘消化。工服上结出片片汗碱，而那些曾经如“天书”般复杂的规程与管线，也在他脑海中逐渐清晰起来。</span><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他以双脚丈量厂房的每一个角落，一步步将理论落到实地。正是这段</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“用脚步学运行”</span></span></strong><span leaf="">的日子，让他逐渐找回自信。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);margin: -3px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="transform: rotateZ(315deg);-webkit-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-moz-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-o-transform: rotateZ(315deg);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 26px;height: 26px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 7px;border-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);background-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 3px inset;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 4px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(95, 156, 239);letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">在实战中淬火成钢</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(178, 210, 240);height: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">蜕变始于赛场，也扎根于日常。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">珠海电厂运行值班员人才济济，在先前两届气电集团燃气轮机运行值班员职业技能大赛中，珠海电厂有三人斩获金牌，多人获评“气电集团技术能手”。群英环绕，但朱贺没有畏缩，反而燃起斗志：“别人能行，我咋就不行？不蒸馒头争口气！”这位东北小伙子暗暗下了决心。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iadbt4yUfUTQZ0cjcGIMTwQdHkDxUPDppx8LXLHDetneib5FTgh91fzfVUCCVsicTiaYmTlIsqp1nl6EM2gIOic0JSmEb7oq4LdVG7I/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他清楚，参赛靠的是硬实力，而实力只能从千锤百炼中来。于是，朱贺把每一次值班都当作实战演练。执行操作票时，他不仅按步骤操作，更反推每一步背后的原理；在仿真机上模拟事故处理时，他不满足于排除故障，更要追问根本原因，思考如何优化处置流程。这种</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">深入骨髓的求索</span></span></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">习惯</span></span></strong><span leaf="">，让他的技能飞速精进。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">渐渐地，他在各级技能竞赛中崭露头角：从珠海电厂第十一届职业技能大赛二等奖，到2023年气电集团燃气轮机运行值班员职业技能大赛二等奖，他的成长轨迹清晰而坚实。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">凭借这股韧劲，朱贺从一名普通巡检员，一步步成长为一名年轻的运行值长，肩负起8小时值班周期内全厂生产运行的总调度职责。2024年，他获评气电集团“青年科技英才”。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);margin: -3px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="transform: rotateZ(315deg);-webkit-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-moz-transform: rotateZ(315deg);-o-transform: rotateZ(315deg);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 26px;height: 26px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-style: solid;border-width: 7px;border-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);background-color: rgb(43, 166, 225);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 3px inset;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 4px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(95, 156, 239);letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">以行者之姿攀登技能高峰</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(178, 210, 240);height: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">2025年9月，中国海油第十三届职业技能竞赛燃气轮机运行值班员竞赛拉开帷幕。经过珠海电厂内部的层层比拼，朱贺拿到大赛入场券。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">此次竞赛，各家单位选派的都是电力板块运行值班员团队中的佼佼者，竞争激烈。备赛时间紧、任务重，朱贺为自己制订了严苛的“三阶段”计划：备赛前期“吃透”设备原理，将燃机、余热锅炉、辅机系统等上千个知识点融会贯通；中期扎根仿真机室，反复练习机组启停、事故处理，将操作流程锤炼成肌肉记忆；后期则通过海量刷题，全面“清零”知识盲点。公司也全力支持，邀请获奖员工传授经验。朱贺和参赛同伴在备赛期间补短板提弱项，相互提升，收获了深厚的友谊。</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: center;margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.49138804457953394" data-s="300,640" data-w="987" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iafcPqdN9oUae8GNjGnraXJmGV4HnQHQUI9LsmfXZCJACNe8AqBIya87PLlxS3LxDtkpNz6CjIxEEbQer7vcgBhC8tlSSl7fA6g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section><section style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“题目内容多、答题时间紧，非常考验日常经验的积累，几乎没有复查的时间，落笔就得是答案。”朱贺回忆道。最终，凭借着日复一日积累的扎实功底与赛场上的冷静发挥，</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">他在43名参赛选手中脱颖而出。</span></span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">夺冠后，朱贺一如既往的谦逊平静：</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 87, 164);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“我们能成功，是因为有这样的好团队。不论谁得第一，都是我们共同的荣誉。”</span></span></strong><span leaf="">在他看来，金牌不是终点，而是新的起点。“没有什么赛场的黑马，只有日复一日的积累。保障机组安全稳定运行，才是我们最重要的赛场。”</span></p></section><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style=