                <![CDATA[ <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><section style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.8;padding: 0px 7px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 1 auto;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.20055710306406685" data-s="300,640" data-w="1077" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wpgKmKoa7iad6zIjPU1FAZZnibrAWyJGsItBdQwkWdRFqCVIvt5Mv4O7L50lC5d4rpmxkgib66AqP3lf445iatG5eyPlPxIZl3cQGlRoKWIk5Jg/640?wx_fmt=gif"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 574px;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 1 auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;width: 574px;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.42407407407407405" data-s="300,640" data-w="1080" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 600px" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wpgKmKoa7iad3UDfyu01aLBib6pBvm3wTbYzNregrvaqGarpCoGx8ibMdrC7CFhxJUVzS0MpdU3t0I5MZWViaAic1f85Plm2kU7nYNkY0u8U7NAQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgb(255, 244, 191) 0%, rgb(255, 255, 255) 100%);border-width: 0px;border-radius: 15px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto;padding: 10px 15px 20px;"><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(113, 65, 16);line-height: 1.8;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 5px;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">甘棠遗爱，典出《诗经·国风·召南·甘棠》：“蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿伐，召伯所茇。”意思是茂盛又浓密的甘棠树，不要修剪不要砍伐，召伯曾经住在树下。</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">后世多用这一成语表达对贤官廉吏的爱戴或怀念。</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><section style="justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgb(249, 243, 238);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section><section style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(153, 113, 77);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“遗爱”意为遗留仁惠，强调德政流传后世。《汉书·叙传》有“没世遗爱，民有余思”的记载。北宋苏轼作《遗爱亭记》来赞颂即将离任的黄州知州徐君猷“未尝怒也，而民不犯；未尝察也，而吏不欺”的政绩。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">百姓对甘棠树爱护有加，意在感戴召伯遗留下来的恩泽。召伯，也称“召公”，姓姬名奭，西周宗室，助武王伐纣，后辅佐成、康二王，与周公旦分陕而治，管理陕地以西地区。召伯为官清廉，巡行乡邑时，体恤百姓农忙劳苦，不愿占用民房或打扰地方官府。一天，召伯巡行至岐山脚下一处村庄，正值炎日当空，就选择在郊外一棵甘棠树下听讼决狱、处理政务，太阳落山后，便在树下搭建草棚，休憩过夜，后成为处理政务的经常之所。在他的治理下，百姓各得其所、安居乐业。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">召伯去世后，百姓因怀念他的仁政，将曾为他遮阴的甘棠树视为勤政爱民的象征，世代保护，禁止砍伐、折枝，并创作《甘棠》一诗表达敬仰。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">“甘棠遗爱”也是政绩为民而树、为民造福的生动注解。</span></strong><span leaf="">历史上不乏因政绩卓异而被百姓怀念的贤官廉吏。春秋时期，子产主持郑国政务，封沟洫，作丘赋，为民求生，为国理财；求贤使能，不毁乡校，倾听民意，闻过而改。有人曾经向他问政，子产回答说：“政如农功，日夜思之，思其始而成其终。”意思是从政要像农民种地一样上心，播种过后，日夜操心，一开始思虑周全，最后才能成功。子产去世时，郑国百姓“丁壮号哭，老人儿啼”，说：“子产去我死乎！民将安归？”孔子闻之痛哭，称他为“古之遗爱也”。北宋剡县令过昱也是一位贤官，他在饥荒年景拿出自己俸禄中的麦子作为种子，帮助饥民重新耕种，救民无数，去世后百姓谈到他，无不恻然泣下。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">德惟善政，政在养民，甘棠遗爱，民之所思。</span></strong><span leaf="">清代诗人薛成兑作七绝《召伯甘棠》云：“蔽芾诗章留古今，召公仁政得民心。甘棠剪伐犹知护，足见当年遗爱深。”我们应树立全心全意为人民服务的政绩观，不求急功近利的“显绩”，创造泽被后人的“潜绩”，不追逐空想，不贪图虚名，用真切可感的善政得人心、暖人心。</span></p></section><section style="text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;"><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px;color: rgb(118, 115, 115);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf="">来源</span><span style="color: rgb(118, 115, 115);box-sizing: border-box;"><span leaf=""> | </span></span><span leaf="">中央纪委国家监委网站</span></span></p><section style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.8;box-sizing: